events.name: International Women's Day Monastir -IWD 2020-
events.description:
As the situation with the coronavirus (COVID-19) develops, we want to help people stay safe, informed and connected. So, we've decided to cancel the IWD's physical event. It's sad that we won't be able to gather as a developer community but your health and safety is our priority.
It's a two days event ;)
The first day has two parts :
1. Will inspire you to "Think Equal" and how to solve "Gender Equality" in order to encourage women and empower them in the STEM world.
2. Will deal with "Women's online safety" to reduce hacking and improve our online skills.
The second day will launch different workshops about various technologies.
In between, we are organizing a #Hackathon / #Ideathon
Please stay at home and be safe ^_^
#StaySafe, #StayAtHome #StayInformed #StayConnected #IAmRemarkable #VirtualSanity
